{"version": 3, "term": {"cols": 132, "rows": 44}, "title": "tael \u2014 AI-agent-native observability"}
[0.1, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H"]
[1.6, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;37m  \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557 \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557 \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557\u2588\u2588\u2557     \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;37m  \u255a\u2550\u2550\u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u255d\u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u2588\u2588\u2557\u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u255d\u2588\u2588\u2551     \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;37m     \u2588\u2588\u2551   \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2551\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557  \u2588\u2588\u2551     \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;37m     \u2588\u2588\u2551   \u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u2588\u2588\u2551\u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u255d  \u2588\u2588\u2551     \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;37m     \u2588\u2588\u2551   \u2588\u2588\u2551  \u2588\u2588\u2551\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;37m     \u255a\u2550\u255d   \u255a\u2550\u255d  \u255a\u2550\u255d\u255a\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u255d\u255a\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u255d\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[0;90mAI-agent-native observability \u00b7 OTLP traces \u00b7 logs \u00b7 metrics\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# One binary \u2014 server + client. `tael serve` runs OTLP gRPC :4317,\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.2, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# the REST API :7701, and the tiered storage engine (hot\u2192warm\u2192cold).\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael serve &\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.5, "o", "\u001b[0;90m[tael] tael-backend storage ready \u00b7 OTLP :4317 \u00b7 API :7701\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Health check \u2014 every command speaks JSON by default\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael server status --format json\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.5, "o", "{\"response\":\"ok\",\"status\":\"healthy\"}\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Ingest OpenTelemetry traces from sample microservices + an LLM call\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael-test\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.5, "o", "connecting to tael server at http://127.0.0.1:4317\r\n  sent: healthy API request (3 spans)\r\n  sent: slow database query (2 spans)\r\n  sent: error in payment service (3 spans)\r\n  sent: fan-out to downstream services (4 spans)\r\n  sent: burst of fast requests (10 spans)\r\n  sent: LLM chat request (gen_ai.*) (2 spans)\r\n\r\ndone \u2014 use `tael query traces` or `tael services` to inspect\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Which services are reporting, and how healthy are they?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael services --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.0, "o", "+----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------+\r\n| Service              | Spans | Traces | Avg Duration (ms) | Error Rate |\r\n+========================================================================+\r\n| api-gateway          | 30    | 30     | 227.3             | 6.67%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| order-service        | 4     | 4      | 450.0             | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| user-service         | 4     | 4      | 42.5              | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| llm-proxy            | 2     | 2      | 1790.0            | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| payment-service      | 2     | 2      | 310.0             | 100.00%    |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| notification-service | 2     | 2      | 45.0              | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| auth-service         | 2     | 2      | 8.0               | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| cart-service         | 2     | 2      | 15.0              | 0.00%      |\r\n+----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Recent traces across every service\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael query traces --last 1h --format table --limit 10\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.2, "o", "+---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------+\r\n| Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service     | Operation               | Duration (ms) | Status | LLM                                  |\r\n+==========================================================================================================================================+\r\n| 8b4ef3e8e60e\u2026 | 2ccc97bbe9ba3f41 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /ping          | 29.0          | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| bf917ec93cb8\u2026 | b5ac6252b8d973dc | api-gateway | HTTP GET /config        | 26.0          | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| fde27643325a\u2026 | 656891ad8adbbc7e | api-gateway | HTTP GET /users/me      | 23.0          | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 4215dba28ee9\u2026 | 3b417259bdeb06f4 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /api/v1/status | 20.0          | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| b2d556d658d2\u2026 | 1c3fa31c68089213 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /health        | 17.0          | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 26a1d66b3cf6\u2026 | 9b373ed778dbea58 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /ping          | 14.0          | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| c624600f906b\u2026 | ddbdb4d0f31289a2 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /config        | 11.0          | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 35c69706f80d\u2026 | c5fb2188da79c203 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /users/me      | 8.0           | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 2b8896ec1a5b\u2026 | f422267aaeada088 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /api/v1/status | 5.0           | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 1267e7807edf\u2026 | 56cb94629216c86f | llm-proxy   | chat anthropic          | 1790.0        | ok     | claude-opus-4-7 \u00b7 1620 tok \u00b7 $0.0213 |\r\n+---------------+------------------+-------------+-------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# What's broken? Filter to error traces\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael query traces --status error --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.0, "o", "+---------------+------------------+-----------------+---------------------+---------------+--------+\r\n| Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service         | Operation           | Duration (ms) | Status |\r\n+===================================================================================================+\r\n| a77080a6eb68\u2026 | 5d6e49f4bba256cd | payment-service | payment.charge      | 310.0         | error  |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-----------------+---------------------+---------------+--------|\r\n| a77080a6eb68\u2026 | 9b2405d1df72444b | api-gateway     | HTTP POST /checkout | 340.0         | error  |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-----------------+---------------------+---------------+--------|\r\n| 6a8d2d8e1f5d\u2026 | fcb3dd45dc902b81 | payment-service | payment.charge      | 310.0         | error  |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-----------------+---------------------+---------------+--------|\r\n| 6a8d2d8e1f5d\u2026 | beabecf720a6acb6 | api-gateway     | HTTP POST /checkout | 340.0         | error  |\r\n+---------------+------------------+-----------------+---------------------+---------------+--------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Where's the latency? Spans slower than 500ms\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael query traces --min-duration 500ms --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.0, "o", "+---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------+\r\n| Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service       | Operation                   | Duration (ms) | Status | LLM                                  |\r\n+================================================================================================================================================+\r\n| 1267e7807edf\u2026 | 56cb94629216c86f | llm-proxy     | chat anthropic              | 1790.0        | ok     | claude-opus-4-7 \u00b7 1620 tok \u00b7 $0.0213 |\r\n|---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 9df778effa5a\u2026 | b00ac9dae5b8e7c8 | order-service | SELECT orders JOIN products | 780.0         | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 1267e7807edf\u2026 | 7039e666d13b8a28 | api-gateway   | POST /v1/chat               | 1850.0        | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 9df778effa5a\u2026 | b7f6ab317abaf156 | api-gateway   | HTTP GET /orders            | 820.0         | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| e6a6989a049c\u2026 | 29de6166794b974c | llm-proxy     | chat anthropic              | 1790.0        | ok     | claude-opus-4-7 \u00b7 1620 tok \u00b7 $0.0213 |\r\n|---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 049cea27bff1\u2026 | 23134c32fc061b23 | order-service | SELECT orders JOIN products | 780.0         | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| e6a6989a049c\u2026 | 3c016c7d2c67a49f | api-gateway   | POST /v1/chat               | 1850.0        | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 049cea27bff1\u2026 | c3e44e8415060112 | api-gateway   | HTTP GET /orders            | 820.0         | ok     | -                                    |\r\n+---------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# NEW \u2014 filter by any span attribute (repeatable)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael query traces --attribute http.route=/checkout --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.0, "o", "+---------------+------------------+-------------+---------------------+---------------+--------+\r\n| Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service     | Operation           | Duration (ms) | Status |\r\n+===============================================================================================+\r\n| a77080a6eb68\u2026 | 9b2405d1df72444b | api-gateway | HTTP POST /checkout | 340.0         | error  |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+---------------------+---------------+--------|\r\n| 6a8d2d8e1f5d\u2026 | beabecf720a6acb6 | api-gateway | HTTP POST /checkout | 340.0         | error  |\r\n+---------------+------------------+-------------+---------------------+---------------+--------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# NEW \u2014 LLM observability: full-text search over gen_ai prompt/completion\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.2, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# payloads. Typed spans carry model, token counts, and cost.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael query traces --text \"OTLP\" --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.2, "o", "+---------------+------------------+-------------+----------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------+\r\n| Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service     | Operation      | Duration (ms) | Status | LLM                                  |\r\n+=================================================================================================================================+\r\n| 1267e7807edf\u2026 | 56cb94629216c86f | llm-proxy   | chat anthropic | 1790.0        | ok     | claude-opus-4-7 \u00b7 1620 tok \u00b7 $0.0213 |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+----------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| 1267e7807edf\u2026 | 7039e666d13b8a28 | api-gateway | POST /v1/chat  | 1850.0        | ok     | -                                    |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+----------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| e6a6989a049c\u2026 | 29de6166794b974c | llm-proxy   | chat anthropic | 1790.0        | ok     | claude-opus-4-7 \u00b7 1620 tok \u00b7 $0.0213 |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+----------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| e6a6989a049c\u2026 | 3c016c7d2c67a49f | api-gateway | POST /v1/chat  | 1850.0        | ok     | -                                    |\r\n+---------------+------------------+-------------+----------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Pull the full failing trace \u2014 span tree, attributes, events \u2014 as JSON\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael get trace 6a8d2d8e1f5d\u2026 --format json\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.5, "o", "{\r\n  \"span_count\": 3,\r\n  \"spans\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"attributes\": {\r\n        \"http.method\": \"POST\",\r\n        \"http.route\": \"/checkout\",\r\n        \"http.status_code\": \"500\"\r\n      },\r\n      \"duration_ms\": 340.0,\r\n      \"end_time\": \"2026-05-26T02:49:29.431602Z\",\r\n      \"events\": [],\r\n      \"kind\": \"internal\",\r\n      \"operation\": \"HTTP POST /checkout\",\r\n      \"parent_span_id\": null,\r\n      \"service\": \"api-gateway\",\r\n      \"span_id\": \"beabecf720a6acb6\",\r\n      \"start_time\": \"2026-05-26T02:49:29.091602Z\",\r\n      \"status\": \"error\",\r\n      \"trace_id\": \"6a8d2d8e1f5d8b03f131edd8d1ebc771\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"attributes\": {},\r\n      \"duration_ms\": 15.000064,\r\n      \"end_time\": \"2026-05-26T02:49:29.109604Z\",\r\n      \"events\": [],\r\n      \"kind\": \"internal\",\r\n      \"operation\": \"cart.validate\",\r\n      \"parent_span_id\": \"beabecf720a6acb6\",\r\n      \"service\": \"cart-service\",\r\n      \"span_id\": \"f37d0a832277351e\",\r\n      \"start_time\": \"2026-05-26T02:49:29.094604Z\",\r\n      \"status\": \"ok\",\r\n      \"trace_id\": \"6a8d2d8e1f5d8b03f131edd8d1ebc771\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"attributes\": {\r\n        \"error.type\": \"PaymentDeclined\",\r\n        \"payment.provider\": \"stripe\"\r\n      },\r\n      \"duration_ms\": 310.000128,\r\n      \"end_time\": \"2026-05-26T02:49:29.421604Z\",\r\n      \"events\": [\r\n        {\r\n          \"attributes\": {\r\n            \"exception.message\": \"Card declined: insufficient funds\",\r\n            \"exception.type\": \"PaymentDeclinedException\"\r\n          },\r\n          \"name\": \"exception\",\r\n          \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-26T02:49:34.091602Z\"\r\n        }\r\n      ],\r\n      \"kind\": \"internal\",\r\n      \"operation\": \"payment.charge\",\r\n      \"parent_span_id\": \"beabecf720a6acb6\",\r\n      \"service\": \"payment-service\",\r\n      \"span_id\": \"fcb3dd45dc902b81\",\r\n      \"start_time\": \"2026-05-26T02:49:29.111604Z\",\r\n      \"status\": \"error\",\r\n      \"trace_id\": \"6a8d2d8e1f5d8b03f131edd8d1ebc771\"\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"trace_id\": \"6a8d2d8e1f5d8b03f131edd8d1ebc771\"\r\n}\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# NEW \u2014 one-shot health digest over a window (traces, services, errors,\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.2, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# log severity, metric volume) \u2014 built for an agent to read in a glance.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael summarize --last 1h --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.5, "o", "Summary \u2014 last 3600s, service: (all)\r\n\r\nTraces\r\n+--------------+-----------+\r\n| Metric       | Value     |\r\n+==========================+\r\n| Spans        | 48        |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Traces       | 30        |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Errors       | 4         |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Error rate   | 8.33%     |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Avg duration | 273.5 ms  |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| p50          | 27.5 ms   |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| p95          | 1790.0 ms |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| p99          | 1850.0 ms |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Max          | 1850.0 ms |\r\n+--------------+-----------+\r\n\r\nTop services\r\n+----------------------+-------+------------+----------+\r\n| Service              | Spans | Error Rate | p95 (ms) |\r\n+======================================================+\r\n| api-gateway          | 30    | 6.67%      | 1386.5   |\r\n|----------------------+-------+------------+----------|\r\n| order-service        | 4     | 0.00%      | 780.0    |\r\n|----------------------+-------+------------+----------|\r\n| user-service         | 4     | 0.00%      | 60.0     |\r\n|----------------------+-------+------------+----------|\r\n| notification-service | 2     | 0.00%      | 45.0     |\r\n|----------------------+-------+------------+----------|\r\n| payment-service      | 2     | 100.00%    | 310.0    |\r\n+----------------------+-------+------------+----------+\r\n\r\nTop error operations\r\n+-----------------+---------------------+--------+\r\n| Service         | Operation           | Errors |\r\n+================================================+\r\n| api-gateway     | HTTP POST /checkout | 2      |\r\n|-----------------+---------------------+--------|\r\n| payment-service | payment.charge      | 2      |\r\n+-----------------+---------------------+--------+\r\n\r\nLogs\r\n+----------+-------+\r\n| Severity | Count |\r\n+==================+\r\n| total    | 0     |\r\n|----------+-------|\r\n| error    | 0     |\r\n|----------+-------|\r\n| warn     | 0     |\r\n|----------+-------|\r\n| info     | 0     |\r\n|----------+-------|\r\n| debug    | 0     |\r\n+----------+-------+\r\n\r\nMetrics\r\n+--------------+-------+\r\n| Metric       | Value |\r\n+======================+\r\n| Points       | 0     |\r\n|--------------+-------|\r\n| Unique names | 0     |\r\n+--------------+-------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# NEW \u2014 read-only SQL straight over the telemetry tables\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael query sql \"SELECT service, COUNT(*) AS spans, ROUND(AVG(duration_ms),1) AS avg_ms FROM spans GROUP BY service ORDER BY spans DESC LIMIT 5\"\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.2, "o", "+--------+----------------------+-------+\r\n| avg_ms | service              | spans |\r\n+=======================================+\r\n| 227.3  | api-gateway          | 30    |\r\n|--------+----------------------+-------|\r\n| 450.0  | order-service        | 4     |\r\n|--------+----------------------+-------|\r\n| 42.5   | user-service         | 4     |\r\n|--------+----------------------+-------|\r\n| 45.0   | notification-service | 2     |\r\n|--------+----------------------+-------|\r\n| 310.0  | payment-service      | 2     |\r\n+--------+----------------------+-------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# NEW \u2014 correlate stitches one trace across spans, logs, and metrics\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael correlate --trace 6a8d2d8e1f5d\u2026 --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.2, "o", "Trace 6a8d2d8e1f5d8b03f131edd8d1ebc771\r\n  spans: 3  errors: 2  duration: 340.0 ms\r\n  services: api-gateway, cart-service, payment-service\r\n  window: 2026-05-26T02:49:29.091602+00:00 \u2192 2026-05-26T02:49:29.431602+00:00\r\n\r\nLogs: (none)\r\n\r\nMetrics: (none in trace window)\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Agents annotate traces \u2014 and can pin a note to a specific span\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael comment add 6a8d2d8e1f5d\u2026 'Stripe 402 \u2014 card declined' --author oncall-bot\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.3, "o", "\u001b[0;90mcomment added by oncall-bot\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael comment add 6a8d2d8e1f5d\u2026 'Card expired. Closing.' --author triage-agent --span-id fcb3dd45dc90\u2026\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.3, "o", "\u001b[0;90mcomment added by triage-agent (span fcb3dd45dc90\u2026)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael comment list 6a8d2d8e1f5d\u2026 --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.0, "o", "[2026-05-26 02:49:34.842797] oncall-bot: Stripe returned 402 \u2014 card declined, not a system fault\r\n[2026-05-26 02:49:35.016041] triage-agent (span fcb3dd45dc902b81): Confirmed: customer card expired. Closing.\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Wire it into Claude Code \u2014 the skill auto-loads when you debug here\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u276f\u001b[0m tael skill where\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
